{"tid":1747802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 唔好衰比人睇 全世界都睇緊呢個區選","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T17:28:25.000Z","uid":77666,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"31e7e06f7f50ea07f8725c6086cf22eff1e83958","tid":1747802,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"由反送中開始 之後演變成警暴 濫捕 <br />\n無數人既年青人為左呢個民主運動斷送自己既前途 可能面對係十年既刑期 <br />\n更加有老人家 小朋友 記者 無辜受害<br />\n到而家 我地終於有機會<br />\n可以用自己既選擇去反映自己既訴求 話比垃圾政府聽<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n而家 你有一票係手 <br />\n可以用你神聖既一票去懲罰一班曾經出賣你 出賣香港人既建制派 <br />\n佢地點樣支持反送中 點樣支持緊急法 點樣支持蒙面法<br />\n若果 你投白票 射落海 放生呢班仆街建制派 <br />\n你代表放棄左一班一直默默付出 堅守價值既年青人<br />\n亦話比全世界聽「香港唔值得人幫」<br />\n聽日 就好好地運用神票既一票 打場靚既仗<br />\n話比全世界既人聽<br />\n「香港人 努力緊 請一齊幫助我地」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你若放棄 誰佑我城<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n附上一張18區侯選人名單 (唔想諗 就直接投佢地)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXAPspQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXAPspQ.jpg&h=e527346c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11814be1cd626666174530b6af8e85b04c58f8d2","tid":1747802,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c1f7c3d536d220e2c118b1263ef3aaf1d19e4f","tid":1747802,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8d063c9f0827a4689c08782a717ccc82810965","tid":1747802,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58dd4f4cb30f7815c0fcc3744cf87245b6e5e9d","tid":1747802,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11